Go to AWS Console → Secrets Manager → Secrets
Find rsvp/admin_credentials (created by Terraform)
Click it → Retrieve secret value → Edit
Choose Plaintext and enter a JSON object:

{
  "username": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "YourStrongPassword1",
  "flask_secret_key": "some-long-random-string",
  "ngrok_authtoken": "your-ngrok-token"
}